"/index.php/Jon_Roxton\" title=\"Jon Roxton\">Jon Roxton</a><sup>1</sup></li>\n<li>Three unnamed <a href=\"/index.php/Lord\" title=\"Lord\">lords</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Landed_knight\" title=\"Landed knight\">landed knights</a><sup>1</sup></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td class=\"navbox-abovebelow\" style=\";\" colspan=\"2\"><div>\n<p><sup>1</sup>Died during the <a href=\"/index.php/Second_Battle_of_Tumbleton\" title=\"Second Battle of Tumbleton\">Second Battle of Tumbleton</a>\n<sup>2</sup>Survived the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>\n<sup>3</sup>Died by <a href=\"/index.php/Poison\" title=\"Poison\">poison</a> after the Second Battle of Tumbleton\n<sup>4</sup>Died the day after the Second Battle of Tumbleton of a wound taken in the battle\n</p>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404113946\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.095 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.294 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1236/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 17811/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 17153/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 4326/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 17/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 3620/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.180/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.74 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  276.805      1 -total\n 91.73%  253.920      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 91.16%  252.322      1 Template:Infobox\n 10.05%   27.818     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  4.40%   12.186      4 Template:Infobox_label\n  3.56%    9.849      5 Template:Ref\n  3.06%    8.468      1 Template:Caltrops\n  2.83%    7.833      1 Template:Navbox\n  2.33%    6.461      5 Template:Ref/core